  + [wisdom_register] is Codex should add Boundary Faculty Inspection as the next first-point check for identity, fair representation, and safety boundary integrity
  + [caution_register] is boundary inspection runtime must not overclaim identity truth, boundary safety, orthogonality, or protected-work permission
  + [balance_register] is stable because Task_057 completed with tests and separate truth/security/feedback dispositions visible
